{"tid":239190,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【港股前瞻】傳中央擬出手維穩 分析指港股勁唔駛托","createTime":"2017-05-11T13:32:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T16:56:39.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6feb83cca32407a66551505f457999c3538878c0","tid":239190,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T13:32:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/91zg371.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F91zg371.jpg&h=bdb0166b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有報道指中央維穩之手七一前會伸延至港股，惟大市對消息反應不大，分析亦認為港股毋須中央支持。<br />\n<br />\n繼日前傳出中央會在下周日及周一的「一帶一路高峰論壇」期間入市維穩A股後，彭博再引述消息，指中央制定了在七一回歸前，由中資背景公司入市穩定港股的計劃，以便在領導人訪港及新任特首就職前營造良好氣氛。報道指計劃已準備就緒，資金有需要時會入市，但資金規模及入市條件等詳情則通通欠奉。<br />\n<br />\n恒指對消息無甚反應，分析普遍亦認為中央無必要干預港股，富昌金融研究部總監譚朗蔚指港股本身走勢強勁，料恒指可「趷下趷下又上啲」，因騰訊等強股可帶領大市再升，恒指暫時可上望25600點，反而A股較港股更需維穩。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，港股表現遠較內地股市為佳，恒指年初至周四累計升14%，而成份股主要為本港及美國上市中資股的MSCI中國指數，周四更創21個月高，收報69點，年初至周四累計升18%。反觀滬綜指及滬深300指數，年初至周四分別跌1.4%及微升1.4%。另外，MSCI中國指數市值更已超越滬深300指數，為2008年後首次。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56681963&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170511\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56681963%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170511&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=93270134\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56681963%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170511&h=3bdfede4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56681963&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170511</a>"},{"pid":"d1b49edb811a9fc76d4a1ff9980eba9a95db6048","tid":239190,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T13:37:06.000Z","msg":"支那顧掂自己個垃圾上證綜合先啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9426a545ed09ca51e53f5a77aa5e6cf27339a430","tid":239190,"uid":59700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T16:26:45.000Z","msg":"維穩到2047啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n推到今年上到20萬點 慶祝20周年回歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb6207e96a74c6ebfa51565cd4a3dcfee57c0ae5","tid":239190,"uid":1544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T16:47:51.000Z","msg":"力托2018 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b862ef59b32345f8735dae6cdea8372233da6df3","tid":239190,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T16:52:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那顧掂自己個垃圾上證綜合先啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be567392ac437bf60cecec25ab2331bfcb73b2f","tid":239190,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T16:56:39.000Z","msg":"到時被人做空<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇你托得幾多<br />\n唔要面死要托，托到自己個泡都爆撚埋"}]}